        <item>
            <title>Diablo IV 首个资料片 10 月推出　《憎恨之躯》将加入新职业和地图等</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/diablo-iv-vessel-of-hatred/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=diablo-iv-vessel-of-hatred</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/diablo-iv-vessel-of-hatred/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 12:00:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Diablo IV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Diablo IV: Vessel of Hatred]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[暗黑破坏神 4：憎恨之躯]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1241879</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>暗黑破坏神 4（Diablo IV) 推出之后已经有一段长时间，继去年 11 月公布推出资料片之后，最近也终于在 Xbox 活动上公布更多有关新资料片的消息。<br /><span id="more-1241879"></span></p><p>Diablo IV: Vessel of Hatred（暗黑破坏神 4：憎恨之躯) 将会延伸 Diablo IV 的故事，涅芮尔拿走灵魂石后，前往纳汉图丛林，期间要与被封印的仇恨之王墨菲斯托对抗，在预告片中可以看到她「黑化」的情节，预计会成为重要的故事伏笔，同时也与上作 Diablo III 有更多剧情上的呼应。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_29777"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mZSfS8EF7qw?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>除了故事延伸之外，游戏将会加入新的职业「魂灵师」，不过进一步消息将要等到 7 月中。另外也会有全新技能和活动。Microsoft 表示，Diablo IV: Vessel of Hatred 已经开始预购，选购豪华版可以获得一系列礼物，包括新宠物、金币和外观等。此外也提供基本游戏和资料片二合一的套装供选购。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/55686683fc1bbbe287ed-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1241880" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/55686683fc1bbbe287ed-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/55686683fc1bbbe287ed.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>来源：<a href="https://diablo4.blizzard.com/zh-tw/vessel-of-hatred"> Blizzard</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/diablo-iv-vessel-of-hatred/game-channel/">Diablo IV 首个资料片 10 月推出　《憎恨之躯》将加入新职业和地图等</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
